title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-04-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-04-2013 MON




Monday, November 04, 2013


Are Americans Becoming Less Self Reliant?



 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest host, Ross Kaminsky. 
Is the American psyche changing so that people actually believe that
  some Obamacare policies are free and the idea of self reliance is in retreat.



 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.



 - 11AM hour

1. Ross urges no vote on amendment 66.
 He also endorses the conservative slate in the Douglas County school board race. 

2. Obama issues executive order on climate change.
